Pfleiderer May Reach Deal With Creditors by End of Next Week

-- B y   N i c h o l a s   C o m f o r t
-- 
2011-03-11T13:57:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-11/pfleiderer-may-reach-deal-with-creditors-by-end-of-next-week.html
  Pfleiderer AG (PFD4)  may reach a deal with
all its creditors on key points of its financing by the end of
next week, the company said in a statement on its website today.  Pfleiderer returned to a profit in  Germany  since the
beginning of the year after reducing capacities as well as
raising prices and is ahead of its own expectations, according
to the statement.    Click here for the statement  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
